elements.title: The Keyboard Company (Wikipedia — did you know?)

elements.title: Amy Gardner (Wikipedia — did you know?)

elements.title: dead cotton (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that dead cotton is immature or underdeveloped cotton that has poor dye affinity and appears as white specks on a dyed fabric?

elements.title: Judita Nagyová (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that during a German charity concert for Ukraine, Slovakian singer Judita Nagyová performed a solo in the finale of Beethoven's Ninth Symphony?

elements.title: Wicked (Wikipedia — did you know?)
elements.contents: ... that Elphaba, the main character in Wicked, is named after L. Frank Baum, who wrote the book that inspired Wicked?

elements.title: Carlton Town F.C. (Wikipedia — did you know?)
